Key0.description: Gives you a random Tier 1 Keychain, equipped in the Specials tab. Click the arrow below your equipment!

Key1.description: Gives you a random Tier 2 Keychain. The balloon animal keychain is my favorite!

Key2.description: Gives you a random Tier 3 Keychain. Good luck, hope you get the one you want!

Key3.description: There's nothing here, and won't be for many many months. Don't buy this, you'll get no keychain!

TalentBook1.description: Gives you this star talent book with random Max Lv between 1 and 100.

EquipmentPendant19.description: This pendant requires Class lv. 20 to equip, and provides good accuracy.

EquipmentPendant20.description: This pendant requires Class lv. 40 to equip, and draws in fish like no other.

EquipmentPendant21.description: This pendant requires Class lv. 80 to equip, and it reeks of both life and death.

EquipmentPendant22.description: This pendant requires Class lv. 110 to equip, and monsters nearby shudder at the sight of it.

EquipmentPendant23.description: This pendant requires Class lv. 140 to equip, and makes you at one with nature and all its splendor.

EquipmentRings21.description: This ring requires Class Lv. 15 to equip, and provides good defence.

EquipmentRings20.description: This ring requires Class Lv. 40 to equip, and boosts skill efficiency.

EquipmentRings19.description: This ring requires Class Lv. 70 to equip, and gives bonus experience.

EquipmentRings22.description: This ring requires Class Lv. 120 to equip, and has great damage stats.

EquipmentRings18.description: This ring requires Class Lv. 150 to equip, and has the greatest stats.
